                     <interp inst="t18280410-244-person1362" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was with Keys, and saw the prisoner walk up to the truck, and take the box out; it was directed to Mr. Henry Johnston.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was very much intoxicated, and did not know where I was till the next morning.</p>
